{"tid":1845470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原來貓貓細細個都有病==","createTime":"2020-01-27T07:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T10:49:34.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7e9d7f9a61c6a2ee19e8829aa742f6bfb48a70","tid":1845470,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"新聞全文：<br />\n<br />\n在1/24個人直播中，禮志和粉絲分享了自己小時候重病經歷。禮志八歲的時候得了流感，即使吃藥了症狀也沒有改善，病情越來越嚴重，最後媽媽帶她去了全州一家醫院。禮志醒來後只記得，她看見媽媽在病床邊哭，在住首爾的外公幫助下，禮志被轉去了首爾一家更大的醫院，在那裡被診斷出流感併發肺炎、骨髓炎和敗血症，最後動了手術，並住院住了一年才康復。在出院時，禮志問了媽媽那天哭泣的事，媽媽才告訴她，當時醫生告訴她要有心理準備（可能撐不過去 ）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av85162660/?share_source=copy_link&amp;p=1&amp;ts=1580060704&amp;share_medium=iphone&amp;bbid=c2e64223a216b0e109b3b665a5b899a4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav85162660%2F%3Fshare_source%3Dcopy_link%26p%3D1%26ts%3D1580060704%26share_medium%3Diphone%26bbid%3Dc2e64223a216b0e109b3b665a5b899a4&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Ri2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=c5f7566d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av85162660/?share_source=copy_link&amp;p=1&amp;ts=1580060704&amp;share_medium=iphone&amp;bbid=c2e64223a216b0e109b3b665a5b899a4</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/riMoX8h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FriMoX8h.jpg&h=49a4834e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43d1bd4981c1766416d873e0d300c640e59f48b7","tid":1845470,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"依家大個有性病"},{"pid":"8baaed105ed2824f3209f99bd83100d569d0060d","tid":1845470,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"43d1bd4981c1766416d873e0d300c640e59f48b7","tid":1845470,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"依家大個有性病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"支持層主 我琴日都聽講過"},{"pid":"16be377bd93bf9cb08b05d03e003